tle it out against Boris the Bodyguard, Sean the Shaman, and the irritating Exoman. \nAnd then there is the boss\u2026\nSurvive to tell the tale!\n\nEnjoy lavishly rendered scenes, colorful backgrounds and fighting action never before seen in VR.", "short_description": "Get ready to put your fighting skills to the ultimate VR test! This is the karate combat game you definitely don\u2019t want to miss. \nThink you are the PERFECT AGGRESSOR? Well, think again\u2026  Victory can be yours if you battle it out against Boris the Bodyguard, Sean the Shaman, and the irritating Exoman. And then there is the boss\u2026\nSurvive to tell the tale!\n\nEnjoy lavishly rendered scenes, colorful backgrounds and fighting action never before seen in VR."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.truckervr.com/oculus-privacy-policy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "http://www.truckervr.com/terms-of-service.html", "publisher_name": "Trucker VR", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "http://www.truckervr.com/", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": null, "context_topics": [], "external_subscription_type": null, "genres": ["ACTION", "ARCADE", "FIGHTING", "SPORTS"], "has_in_app_ads": null, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": null, "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["GAMEPAD"], "supported_player_modes": [], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "512244817291548"}, "review_messages": [""]}]}, "cover_square_image": {"uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/12410493_192357117984819_3316104460664569856_n.png?stp=dst-png_s360x360&_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=x8BkW9iB3FUQ7kNvgFMrO4S&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYC_pbStD3d7Ogq64ShL0nRKEBvm2J6c246ucqKLVKg5jQ&oe=67792A6F"